examples.en: Bamboo is the panda's staple diet (=main food).
Bamboo is a very vigorous grower.
The furniture is crafted from bamboo.
Bamboo grows in the grove near the house.
This craftsman can make almost anything out of bamboo.
He wore a colossal aigrette, made of bamboo and horsehair.
He made her a toy horse, using just some straw and bamboo twigs.
